Ashihama is a distant island within the Pincers region of the Wushanko Isles, otherwise called the Eastern Lands. Little about it is known, though it is most known for being the original home of The Nightmare of Ashihama, which was created in an ancient ritual by shamans on the island. The Nightmare was eventually driven away from Ashihama by local sirens, led by Shura.
